Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:03.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meet eyes with her for three seconds, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:07.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:09.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something bad happens a week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:12.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:14.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:18.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Yuka met eyes with her and she got a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.76,0:01:27.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:36.86,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone apologizes to me for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:41.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she's got a really strong psychic aura. She's attracting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, even her name is Sadako, like from Ringu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:48.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her parents gave her a pretty blunt name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:06.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to burst your bubble, but I can't see ghosts or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my name's not Sadako, it's Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:13.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written as "breezy child." Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:26.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, everyone's afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:29.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could just fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they get lots of celebrities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.91,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hirano-san, Endo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that was a cheerful hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:52.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:58.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always the center of attention
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's cheerful and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:02.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:05.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:09.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't treat me differently!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:19.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun is the exact opposite of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone flocks around him
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:25.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and forms a clique.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:28.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,At the opening ceremony when I came to high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:46.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're heading to Kitahoro High School, it's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,People only ever apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But he smiled and thanked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:06.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun's been my idol ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:12.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become like him someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to have a test of courage on the day before the closing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:26.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll post this on the bulletin board. Write your name down if you're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to come if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.75,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone? Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sadako's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we'll see real ghosts if she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:39.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't live up to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:43.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I might let everyone down if nothing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:47.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break starts after the closing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And summer break means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,study sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:57.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone want to come to school before the sessions and help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If no one volunteers, I'll choose myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:06.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No one wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma's always doing that sort of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:31.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure we should make her keep picking up tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to do it then, Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:40.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew what I've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:58.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much to do during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I live nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm really bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:05.42,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:12.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so dull, yet he knew what I've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shino-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, now that we're in different classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's class?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:32.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one from grade school or middle school, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:36.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's this guy named Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not just cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's 100% cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:49.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, he's made of cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was bad, he heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was complimenting him. Did he take it the wrong way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what am I supposed to make of what you just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming over there, just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:36.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really had a chance to talk to you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:45.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he likes to talk to people who don't fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:54.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun's such a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He understood what I meant to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He took me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:11.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might have hated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:22.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the time, I've wished I could be cool like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:27.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah, I'm not particularly cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma Sawako, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:48.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever calls me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:54.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is the first time someone {\i1}didn't{\i0}{\fscx50} {\fscx100} misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:09:00.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you talked, you said what was on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.86,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:10.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've been called by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've felt like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:15.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better come to the test of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,550)}It's the first time in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:27.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to quietly write my name on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:34.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be more fun with someone as a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:39.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone would freak out just seeing her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since when were you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may I be a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't {\i1}have{\i0} to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not if you don't really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you talked,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:05.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you said what was on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:11.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to fit in with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:18.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean I was doing it begrudgingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:22.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just like being helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:30.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to warn you though, I can't live up to your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:31.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make real ghosts appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any psychic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're breaking the news now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And our “expectations”?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're so messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}seriously{\i0} messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:56.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Chizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:58.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you crying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:02.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a soft spot for selfless kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're messed up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:07.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do the ghost thing for us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:10.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scare the hell out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They understood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:24.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've changed, even if just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:32.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set out every ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got almost everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So only Sadako's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sadako's—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:01.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to let everyone have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:07.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Those screams...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:52.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, I'm being so useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:55.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try holding some hair in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:13.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was playing a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:20.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the organizer after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you weren't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:29.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wouldn't get as much of a chill if I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:32.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared being alone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:38.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of like nighttime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially during summertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:46.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air, the smell,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:50.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sound of the leaves, the insects' voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I stay here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But— What about the test of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you-know-who,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:10.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we had an odd number of people, so I had to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:22.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san, Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you could have told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:37.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:42.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,good job, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snack time. Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:48.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-They're nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:57.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, you're fitting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fitting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:09.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I— It's thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:17.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you that I could speak my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:21.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I could play a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:25.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually pretty cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:35.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time anyone's ever said that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:43.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:47.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful not to look at you for three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that thing about bringing bad luck—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:51.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:56.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassing me. Don't make me say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He just stopped talking all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:07.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind's falling to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I was just reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:15.99,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So many feelings that're new to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:22.46,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun gives me a lot of new experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:26.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I met Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:28.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's announce the results of the test of courage before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:36.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, you're in the penalty game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never got to the finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka gets first prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You win 60 scrub brushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:49.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the loser, Kazehaya-kun, gets...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:54.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to go out with Sadako-chan for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did he just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:02.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were with Sadako yesterday, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she was making a move on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything but that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you call that a penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:21.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't defend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:37.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll ruin his reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:44.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I was with Kazehaya-kun yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it wasn't anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:56.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he approaches everyone without prejudice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:59.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:03.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to fix misunderstandings now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:10.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I was attracted by his kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:14.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his coolness, his honesty, his outgoingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... {\alpha&HFF}no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They must know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:48.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I've protected his reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:52.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:57.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have to help my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:05.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have done the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:15.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:20.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He might not even look at me after the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:24.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He might not say “good morning” to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He might avoid me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:30.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:36.27,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too happy; I forgot I was used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:42.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What I was like before I met Kazehaya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:47.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said you're the MVP behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:01.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:05.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:15.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stood up for me and brought this to me and talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:17.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:22.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you really understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:25.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:28.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:29.07,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:40.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can expect to see you over the summer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)}Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:53.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're heading to Kitahoro High School, it's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That feeling I had back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the way it's grown until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:13.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will it ever reach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:27.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New term.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:32.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are slowly changing around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:34.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Seating Change
